item.title: Farhan
item.description: Farhan was a DP leader who came any chance he got. He founded the Rocketry GitHub and set the stage for lots of programming that would come.

item.title: Russell
item.description: Russell was the President of Rocketry club during 2024-2025. He is a sigma professional rock climber.

item.title: Graduated Rocket Motors
item.description: Rocket Engines go from A-P. As a general rule, each rocket letter is 2x the power of the previous. For example, B is 2x the power of A.
